These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
House: art-deco, farmhouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, badminton
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| House   | farmhouse  | art-deco |
| Sport       | cricket | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different games are played: poker, snooker
House: palace, modern
1. the modern house is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Game   | poker | snooker |
| House      | modern     | palace  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, january
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | board-games  |
| Birthday   | november | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, roller
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, martial-arts
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Transport   | roller | car   |
| Movie-Genre       | martial-arts | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-5::.
