.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bolivar
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
